---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Culture | The Açai Club" description="Our story, our Run Club, our community. The Açai Club is more than bowls.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative pt-28 pb-24 bg-dark">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-light leading-[0.95]">
        More than<br /><span class="text-beige">a bowl</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 text-grey text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
        The Açai Club started with a simple idea: bring the freshest açai bowls to the UK & build a community around healthy, active living.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section id="culture" class="py-24 bg-dark-surface">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-light mb-8">
            Born from the love of açai
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-grey text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              It started with a trip abroad — our founders discovered açai & got hooked. When they came back to the UK, nothing compared. So they made one from scratch in the kitchen, looked at each other & said: "We could sell this."
            </p>
            <p>
              They started from the back of their office — one fridge, one freezer, a few toppings — & launched on delivery platforms. No store, no staff, just watching a baby cam pointed at the order machine from home.
            </p>
            <p>
              That grew into a store. Then another. Then another. And throughout it all, one thing never changed: the açai is never blended down, never diluted. 140g of pure açai, exactly as it comes — the way almost nobody else does it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl aspect-square overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/ig-bowls-1.jpg" alt="Açai bowls with fresh berries" class="w-full h-full object-cover" /></div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl aspect-square overflow-hidden mt-8"><img src="/images/ig-bowls-3.jpg" alt="Açai bowl topped with fresh fruit" class="w-full h-full object-cover" /></div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl aspect-square overflow-hidden -mt-8"><img src="/images/ig-beaconsfield.jpg" alt="The Açai Club Beaconsfield store" class="w-full h-full object-cover" /></div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl aspect-square overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/ig-reading.jpg" alt="The Açai Club Reading store" class="w-full h-full object-cover" /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-dark">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-light mb-12 text-center">
        The Manifest
      </h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-6">🫐</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-normal text-light mb-3">Never Diluted</h3>
          <p class="text-grey text-sm">We serve 140g of pure açai — never blended down with banana or syrup. That's how almost nobody else does it, & we never will.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-6">🌱</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-normal text-light mb-3">Real Ingredients</h3>
          <p class="text-grey text-sm">No shortcuts on toppings either. Every adaptogen, granola, & protein has been sourced for quality — regardless of cost.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-6">🏃</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-normal text-light mb-3">Active Living</h3>
          <p class="text-grey text-sm">We run, we move, we fuel. Built around an active lifestyle, not just a menu.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-6">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-normal text-light mb-3">Community First</h3>
          <p class="text-grey text-sm">From Run Club to in-store vibes, everything we do is about bringing people together.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Run Club -->
  <section id="run-club" class="py-24 bg-dark-surface">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="font-heading text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-beige mb-4">Every Sunday</p>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-light mb-8">
            Run Club
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-grey text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <p>Every Sunday at 8am, we lace up & run together. It doesn't matter if you're training for a marathon or just getting started — everyone is welcome.</p>
            <p>After the run, come back to the store for a free berry. Because earning your breakfast just hits different.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-10">
            <a href="/app" class="inline-flex px-10 py-4 bg-light text-dark font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm rounded-full hover:bg-light-muted transition-colors">
              Join via App
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-dark-border">
            <div class="text-4xl font-heading font-normal text-light">52</div>
            <p class="text-grey mt-2 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider">Runs/year</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-dark-border">
            <div class="text-4xl font-heading font-normal text-light">5mi</div>
            <p class="text-grey mt-2 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider">Standard</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-dark-border">
            <div class="text-4xl font-heading font-normal text-light">8am</div>
            <p class="text-grey mt-2 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider">Sunday</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-dark-border">
            <div class="text-4xl font-heading font-normal text-light">Free</div>
            <p class="text-grey mt-2 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider">Bowl after</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Press -->
  <section id="press" class="py-24 bg-dark-surface border-t border-dark-border">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-light mb-4">
        Press & Media
      </h2>
      <p class="text-grey text-lg">
        Get in touch at <a href="mailto:press@theacaiclub.com" class="text-beige hover:underline">press@theacaiclub.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
